<td align="center"><b>
<i>Andrena melanochroa</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">Cockerell, 1898</font></b><br>
<small><i>Micrandrena pacifica </i>Ashmead, 1899; <i>Andrena fragariana </i>Graenicher, 1904; <i>Andrena &#40;Micrandrena&#41; vagans </i>Cockerell, 1932</small><p>
